Q1) In the Global Security, I didn&rsquo;t have a TCP port for JNLP agents enabled, which automatically disables the line &ldquo;Launch agent via Java Web Start&rdquo;
Solution:
Manage Jenkins =&gt; Configure Global Security =&gt; Enable security =&gt; TCP port for JNLP agents Set it to either Fixed (for this option also set the port number) or Random.
